    • Constructor Detail

      • GameBoardPane

        GameBoardPane(MapInfoView mapInfoView,
              double width,
              double height,
              GUIViewJavaFX viewJavaFX)
        Create the main window of the GUI. The window is divided in three row, and each row contains the subelements composing the graphic. Every pane is set so that it will not be stretched if different screen resolutions
        Parameters:
        mapInfoView - the current state of the map
        width - the width of the pane
        height - the height of the pane
        viewJavaFX - the GUI instance
